<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #6a1b9a;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .content h2 {
            color: #333333;
        }
        .content p {
            color: #555555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Shopie!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello <%= name %>!</h2>
            <p>Thank you for registering with Shopie. We're thrilled to have you on board.</p>
            <p>Explore our collection of amazing products and enjoy a seamless shopping experience.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
            <p>Happy Shopping!</p>
            <p>Best Regards,<br>The Shopie Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Shopie. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
